{
  "chapter": 44,
  "chapter_summary": "第四十四回「两世为人」。李寻欢藏身于林仙儿衣橱中，被两名闯入的女子发现。其中肥胖的至尊宝是大欢喜女菩萨座下高手，生性好色，欲对李寻欢行不轨；蓝蝎子则因右手被折断之仇而来。至尊宝与蓝蝎子争夺李寻欢，蓝蝎子趁至尊宝不备以蝎尾兵器暗算，至尊宝中剧毒而死。蓝蝎子表明恩怨分明——因伊哭之死本为寻林仙儿算账，但念及李寻欢未取她性命之恩，出手相救。李寻欢穴道已解却未动飞刀，主动伸出右手愿以一臂偿债。蓝蝎子深受震动，长叹「世上竟真有这样的人」，放弃索债离去。李寻欢追出挽留。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们这是什么意思？难道是土匪么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们正是来找你们家小姐的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们是来找我家小姐的？你们认得她！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然认得……不但认得，而且还是好朋友。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然如此，两位为何不早说，害得我还将两位当土匪哩。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们的样子看来难道很像土匪？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位这就不知道了，现在的土匪已经跟以前不一样，有的简直比两位还要斯文，还要漂亮，谁也看不出他的身份来。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你家小姐到哪里去了？请她出来好么？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位来得真不巧，小姐前几天就出门了，只留我一个人在这里看家，两位有什么事，告诉我也是一样。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她什么时候回来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知道……小姐没有说，我怎么敢问？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们一来，她就出门了，我们不来，她天天都在这里，难道她知道我们要来，就躲起来不敢见人么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位既是小姐的朋友，她要知道两位到了，欢喜还来不及，怎么会躲起来呢？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有些人什么人都敢见，就是不敢见朋友，你说奇怪不奇怪？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这也许是因为她对不起朋友的事做得太多了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位真会说笑话，这地方这么小，一个大人就算要躲起来，也没地方躲呀。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦，是么？……这地方我虽然不熟，但我若要躲起来，倒说不定可以找得到地方。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么姑娘除非躲到这衣橱里。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但一个人若躲在衣橱里，岂非闷也要被闷死了，那滋味一定不好受。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，你们家小姐金枝玉叶，自然不肯躲到衣橱里去的……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只不过，你家小姐既然不肯躲到衣橱里，现在衣橱里这人是谁呢？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？……衣橱里有人？怎么连我都不知道？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "衣橱里若没有人，你为什么一直挡在前面呢？难道怕我们偷你们小姐的衣服吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有呀？……我哪里挡在前面……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小妹妹，你虽然很聪明，很会说话，只可惜年纪还是太小了些，要想骗过我们这两个老狐狸，恐怕还要再等几年。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小妹妹，这人是谁呀，睡着了么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他……他是我的表哥。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有趣有趣，有趣极了，我小的时候也常常将我的情人藏在衣橱里，有一次被人发现了，我也说他是我的表哥。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么天下的女孩子都喜欢说自己的情人是表哥呢，难道就不能换个新花样说说么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这还是我第一次……下次我就知道换花样了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位小妹妹倒真是'年轻有为'，看样子连我们都比她差多了，这才真叫做后生可畏。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "林仙儿既然不在这里，我们走吧。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "急什么？我们既然来了，多坐坐又何妨？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小妹妹，你年纪虽小，选择男人的眼光倒真不错。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这地方的男人不多，好的都被小姐挑走了，我也只好将就些。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这样的男人你还不满意么？你看他既不胖，也不瘦，脸长得也不讨人厌，而且看样子对女人很有经验。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他别的倒也还不错，就是太喜欢睡觉，一睡着就不醒。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这也许是因为他太累了……遇着你这样的小狐狸精，他怎么会不累？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他年纪也太大了些。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯，不错，他配你的确嫌太大了些，配我倒刚好。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小妹妹，你若不中意，就把他让给我吧，过两天，我一定找个年轻的来陪你。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人脏得很，常常几个月不洗澡，姑娘千万莫要抱他，他身子不但有跳蚤还有臭虫。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "脏？谁说他脏？何况他身上就算有臭虫也没关系，男人身上的臭虫，一定也有男人的味道。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要有男人味道的东西，我都喜欢。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是……可是他非但又脏又懒，而且还是个酒鬼。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "酒鬼更好，酒量好的男人，才有男子汉气概。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若喜欢喝酒，我就陪你喝酒，有些事喝了酒之后再做更有趣。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有种男人，平时道貌岸然，一本正经，但一见到女人，骨头就轻了，这种男人别人都叫他'色鬼'，却不知这种女人该叫做什么呢？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这种女人也叫做'色鬼'我正是不折不扣的一个女色鬼，只要见到好看的男人，就没法子不动心。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "却不知男人见了你会不会动心？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我虽然胖了些，但懂事的男人都知道，胖女人不但温柔体贴，冬暖夏凉，而且还有种好处。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好处在哪里，你马上就会知道了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我笑你真是色胆包天，连他的脑筋你都敢动。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我为什么不能动他的脑筋？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你可知道他是谁么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你可知道我是谁么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你总不是他的表妹吧。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你可听说过'大欢喜女菩萨'这名字？我就是女菩萨座下的'至尊宝'，只要是男人我就统吃。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若敢吃他，小心吃下去鲠着喉咙，吐不出来。",
      "tone": "警告",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我吃人从来也不吐骨头的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小妹妹，我劝你还是闭上嘴吧，要不是因为我办事前从不愿杀人，免得煞风景，你现在早就连眼睛都闭上了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你难道就不想知道他是谁吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我若想知道，我自己会问他，用不着你操心，何况……我只要他是个男人就够了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "拜托你，帮帮我的忙，把这小丫头弄出去，这地方还不错，我想暂时借用一下，你可不准偷看。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这男人我也要。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "什么？你说什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这男人我也要！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "你敢跟我抢？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "抢定了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "你若真想要他，我们姐妹俩的事总好商量。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不是要他的人，我是要他的命！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "这就更好办了，等我要过他的人，你再要他的命也不迟呀。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "等我要过他的命，你再要他的人吧。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "我虽然很喜欢男人，但对死人却没什么兴趣。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他现在岂非和死人差不多？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "他现在不能动，只不过是因为被人点了穴道，我自然有法子要他动的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "等他能动的时候，我再想要他的命就已迟了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，等他能动的时候，只要他的手一动，你们就再见了！",
      "tone": "悠然",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "你说他是谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他就是小李飞刀！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "我不信，他若真是李寻欢，怎会看上你这么样一个小丫头？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他并没有看上我，是我看上了他，所以才希望你们快杀了他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我家小姐常告诉我，你若看上一个男人，他却看不上你，那么你就宁可要了他的命，也不能让他落到别的女人手上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "想不到这小丫头的心肠竟比我还毒辣。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道你还想要他的人么？你真有这么大的胆子？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "牡丹花下死，做鬼也风流。能和李寻欢这样的名男人做一夜夫妻，就算死也不冤枉了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "但你也不必着急，我要过他的人之后，还是有法子再让你要他的命。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "男人的手若被砍断了，你还有兴趣么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "手断了倒没有什么关系，只要别的地方不断就行了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么我就要他一只手！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "左手还是右手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他折断了我的右手，我也要他的一只右手！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "好，你来吧……但切莫弄得鲜血淋漓的，叫人恶心，用你那根蝎子尾巴随便在他手上螫一下就算了吧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，就这么办。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们真敢这么样对他？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "小妹妹，难道你又心疼了么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "speaker_name": "至尊宝",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "你……你好大的胆子，敢暗算我，我要你的命！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": "char_zhi_zun_bao",
      "text": "中了我蝎尾之毒，走不出七步必死无疑，就算你身子比别人大些，毒性发作慢些，你能再走三步还不倒下，我佩服你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "伊哭就是为了去找林仙儿才会死的，我到这里来，本是为了要找林仙儿算账，和你本无关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "你若想他说话，为什么不解开他的穴道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你虽然废了我的一只手，却未要我的命，总算对我有恩，我这人一生恩怨最分明，你对我有点水之恩，我就不能眼看着你被那猪糟蹋。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我既已还了你的债，你欠我的自然也非还不可，我也只要你一只右手，这总不算过分吧。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你……你这只手怎么忽然能动了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "我本就在运气解穴，只可惜功夫不到家，一直无法冲破最后一关，谁知方才那一跌，却帮了我的忙。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "那么你为何还如此听话，她要你这只手，你就乖乖地伸出来给她你……为何不给她一刀？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "蓝姑娘，你要的实不过分，我也毫无怨言，请。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝蝎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "世上竟真有这样的人……世上竟真有上这样的人……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lan_xie_zi",
      "text": "请等一等。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    }
  ],
